LogFile.FinalText: Amazing how they look alike. That is what many people think about Denmark's two princesses. Marie and Mary show many similarities but they have just as many, if not more, differences. They are both from abroad, they are both born as regular citizens and they have both found a prince from Denmark. Mary is married to crown prince Frederik and Marie to prince Joachim. Their names and appearances are also very similar. They are both modelesque with long, dark hair and big, brown eyes. But despite their many similarities, Mary and Marie are both independent individuals who have lived and still do in their own way which has shaped their values and their characters.
